						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment of 2 plots of land made tax-free after purchase, by <hi rend="bold">Mūvēnda-Pallavaraiyar</hi> of Nalvayal in Śeṅguṉṟa-nāḍu for the daily offerings to the god in the temple of Tiruvālakkōyil-Perumāḷ at Kachchūr in the same <hi rend="italic">nāḍu</hi>, which was a subdivision of Kalattūr-kōttam. </p>						

